}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#33a2559a16abb8d25778e6ec03a1a16c>.
<#33a2559a16abb8d25778e6ec03a1a16c> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/edb8b81b-dd7a-4a29-98ae-a454d2cfddcc>;
