    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#Dataset>, <http://entryscape.com/terms/ServedByDataService>
}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#5d9c7d15832c9e7d5f214026bdbdf4ae>.
<#5d9c7d15832c9e7d5f214026bdbdf4ae> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
