<https://ckan-malmo.dataplatform.se/dataset/75541738-351e-4e97-838e-d4aed5bd2471> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/290/resource/ce429264a6a97cd4bc8687f7a5b0847d>;
