<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#770c41ac13837db4c3537aa3a13ee329>.
<#770c41ac13837db4c3537aa3a13ee329> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/U00490>;
